name: diary_log/6
description: we went to the negotiation meeting with mubans in their main metropolis / our translator ate some served aubergine in the quest room before the meeting and apparently these alien eggplants have intoxicating effects on humans / translator had hallucinations and mistranslated everything we have said while mubans saw the whole scene as an insult / they kicked us out but we are safe in our ship returning home and we will have a talk with him when he wakes up
